quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  34,32,"Waawunoo…ìe townitaninoo…ìe goonga …ìen wi'ani waawanoo…ìe lo'inanoo…ìe …ìen: E ko menen ha…óunoo on feewirgol ko Muhammadu addi kon? onon kay, on woniino too√±u…ìe e bom…ìe bonnoo…ìe."
  34,33,"Sukkunoo…ìe …ìen wi'ana hooree…ìe ma…ì…ìe lo'inunu …ìe townitanii…ìe goonga …ìen: Si ko woni, on sakkor-falina- men e peewal ngal, pewje mon jemma e √±alorma …óen, fewndo yamirayno…óon men yeddugol Alla, rewa tagaa…ìe goo gaanin Makko. ∆Åe suu…ói ninse keeferaaku ma…ì…ìe ngun aduna, nde …ìe yi'unoo lepte …óen, …ìe yananaa wonnde ko …ìe leptetee…ìe. Men wa…ói kolombooje e daa…óe yeddu…ìe …ìen. ∆Åe yo…ìitiraaka ndii njo…ìdi, si wanaa sabu ko …ìe huuwaynoo kon aduna, e rewugol ko woori Alla, faggitoo geddi."
  34,34,"Men imminaali nulaa…óo e saare, mo no hul…ìinira …ìe lepte Alla …óen, si wanaa neeminaa…ìe ma…ì…ìe joomiraa…ìe cemmbe e muyba e jawle …ìen wi'ay: Menen ko men yeddu…ìe ko imminira…óon kon, onon nulaa…ìe …ìen."
  34,35,"Muybu…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen haawiti hino mantoo wi'a: Ko menen …ìuri …óuu…óude jawle e jiidi. Kadi, ko aa∆¥i…óon kon wonnde men leptete, ko fenaande. Men wonaali leptetee…ìe aduna, wanaa fii laakara."
  34,36,"An Nulaa…óo, maakan …ìee mantor…ìe neema mo …ìe okkaa: Joomi am Senii…óo On, Himo ya√±√±ana arsike on, on mo O muuyi, fii ndaarndagol si ontigi yettay Mo maa si o yedday. Himo …ìillina kadi mo O muuyani, fii jarribagol si ontigi mu√±√±oto maa o tikkiray. Kono …ìurr…ìe …óuu…óude e yim…ìe …ìen, …ìe anndaa wonnde Alla ko √ëee√±o: O e…ì…ìirtaa huunde, si wanaa √±ee√±al yottiingal, heddoo ko hommbo faamata ngal e ko hommbo majjetee ngal."
  34,37,"Wanaa jawle mon, wanaa jiidi mon ndi mantorton, woni ko …ìa…ónata on e welayee Alla. Kala non gom…óim…ìe Alla, …ìe golli golle mo∆¥∆¥e, …ìe da√±ay njo…ìdi sowaandi. Jawle …óen, ko nafqirgol …óe fii laawol Alla …ìadnata …óe ka Alla, jiidi ndin kadi, ko si …ìe du'anike ontigi. ∆Åen gom…óim…ìe …ìe golli golle mo∆¥∆¥e, hino woodani …ìe njo…ìdi sowaandi, sabu ko …ìe golli mo∆¥∆¥u…ói kon. Kam…ìe ka ku…ìeeje Aljanna toowu…óe, ko …ìe hoolii…ìe, …ìe hulaa lepte e maayde e dartagol neema."
  34,38,"∆Åen yeddu…ìe tii…ónoray…ìe ha…ótirde e tii…ónagl no yiilira yim…ìe …ìen e Aajeeye Amen …óen, …ìe etoo no faandundeeji ma…ì…ìe laatora, …ìen ko hayru…ìe aduna, leptoytee…ìe laakara."
  34,39,"Maaku an Nulaa…óo: Pellet, Joomi am Senii…óo On, Himo ya√±√±ana arsike on, mo O muuyani e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, O …ìillina mo O muuyi e ma…ì…ìe. Kala non ko wintor…óon e huunde, fii laawol Alla, haray Alla lontinniranay on nde aduna, ye…óugol on ko …ìuri …óum, e mbarjaari teddundi ka laakara. Ko Kanko Alla woni Mo∆¥∆¥o Arsikoowo. Mo …óa…ì…ìay arsike, yo O fewtu Mo Kanko."